headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid PHM and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since January 2021, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 82.8%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, PulteGroup has surged 214% to $133.75 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 18.5% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 7.4%.
